'''2015年委內瑞拉議會選舉'''于2015年12月6日举行<ref>{{cite news|title=Venezuela to hold parliamentary election on Dec. 6|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/06/22/us-venezuela-election-idUSKBN0P21ZH20150622|accessdate=22 June 2015|agency=Reuters|date=22 June 2015|archivedate=2015-09-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924220659/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/06/22/us-venezuela-election-idUSKBN0P21ZH20150622|deadurl=no}}</ref>，反對黨成員曾推測[[委內瑞拉總統|委內瑞拉總統]][[尼古拉斯·马杜罗|尼古拉斯·马杜罗]]可能會暫停選舉；但马杜罗表示即使執政黨處於不利情況下，選舉仍會舉行<ref name=nosuspend>{{cite news|title=Maduro rejects speculation he'll suspend Venezuela elections - Salon.com|url=http://www.salon.com/2015/03/05/maduro_rejects_speculation_hell_suspend_venezuela_elections/|accessdate=9 April 2015|agency=[[Associated_Press|AP]]|date=5 March 2015 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150416125448/http://www.salon.com/2015/03/05/maduro_rejects_speculation_hell_suspend_venezuela_elections/|archivedate=2015年4月16日}}</ref>。

選舉結果顯示執政黨[[委内瑞拉统一社会主义党|委内瑞拉统一社会主义党]]大敗，自1999年以來首次失去國民議會控制權。<ref>[http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-35033778 Venezuela election: Opposition 'wins two-thirds majority'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-35033778 |date=20151209063502 }}, BBC News, 7 December 2015</ref>

==選舉制度==
自2000年開始，[[全国代表大会_(委内瑞拉)|委内瑞拉全国代表大会]]全部167個席位採用[[并立制|并立制]]選出：113個分布於87個選區的議席使用[[多數制|多數制]]；51個分布於[[委内瑞拉行政区划|23個州]]及[[首都區_(委內瑞拉)|首都區]]的議席採用[[封閉式名單|封閉式名單]][[比例代表制|比例代表制]]、席次分配使用[[漢狄法|漢狄法]]；餘下3個議席預留給{{le|委內瑞拉原住民|Indigenous peoples in Venezuela|原住民}}，由其社區選出<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.avn.info.ve/contenido/113-diputados-ser%C3%A1n-electos-voto-nominal-y-51-voto-lista-parlamentarias | title=113 diputados serán electos por voto nominal y 51 por voto lista en parlamentarias | work=Agencia Venezolana de Noticias | date=7 May 2015 | accessdate=9 May 2015 | archivedate=2015-10-22 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151022023104/http://www.avn.info.ve/contenido/113-diputados-ser%C3%A1n-electos-voto-nominal-y-51-voto-lista-parlamentarias | deadurl=no }}</ref>。

==選舉結果==
2015年12月7日午夜，[[全国代表大会_(委内瑞拉)|委内瑞拉全国代表大会]]宣布反對黨[[民主團結圓桌會議|民主團結圓桌會議]]在議會167席中至少取得99席，意味著反對黨已取得勝利；相反執政黨只獲得46席<ref name=ABCNEWS>{{cite news|last1=Dreier|first1=Hannah|title=Venezuela's Opposition Wins Control of National Assembly|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/venezuelas-opposition-wins-control-national-assembly-35616983|accessdate=7 December 2015|agency=[[ABC_News|ABC News]]|date=7 December 2015|archivedate=2015-12-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151207195744/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/venezuelas-opposition-wins-control-national-assembly-35616983|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/the_americas/venezuela-opposition-claims-victory-ahead-of-vote-results/2015/12/06/fd6a36ac-9c90-11e5-9ad2-568d814bbf3b_story.html|title = Venezuela’s opposition wins control of National Assembly|last = |first = |date = 7 December 2015|work = Washington Post|accessdate = 7 December 2015|via = |archivedate = 2015-12-07|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151207215642/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/the_americas/venezuela-opposition-claims-victory-ahead-of-vote-results/2015/12/06/fd6a36ac-9c90-11e5-9ad2-568d814bbf3b_story.html|deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.telesurtv.net/english/news/Live-Updates-Venezuelas-National-Assembly-Elections-20151206-0008.html|title = Live Updates: Venezuelan's Wait for Results in Tight National Assembly Elections|last = |first = |date = |work = TeleSurTV|accessdate = 7 December 2015|via = |archivedate = 2015-12-09|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151209172937/http://www.telesurtv.net/english/news/Live-Updates-Venezuelas-National-Assembly-Elections-20151206-0008.html|deadurl = no}}</ref>，選民投票率超過70%<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-12-06/venezuelans-to-vote-in-polls-seen-handing-congress-to-opposition|title = Venezuela Opposition Won Majority of National Assembly Seats|last = |first = |date = 7 December 2015|work = Bloomberg|accessdate = 7 December 2015|via = |archivedate = 2015-12-09|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151209052906/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-12-06/venezuelans-to-vote-in-polls-seen-handing-congress-to-opposition|deadurl = no}}</ref>。

